  "remarks": "TAi.144 Designation: Na'ib Amir (Deputy Commander). Heading the Haqqani Network (TE.H.12.12.) as of late 2012. Son of Jallaloudine Haqani (TI.H.40.01). Belongs to Sultan Khel section, Zadran tribe of Garda Saray of Paktia province, Afghanistan. Believed to be in the Afghanistan/Pakistan border area.; Listing: Listed by the UN 1267 Committee on 13 Sept. 2007 (amended 22 April 2013)",
